00:35:06.840 --> 00:35:12.620
food stamp would be worth $8 in the market,
and I think it's a brilliant little variation.

00:35:12.620 --> 00:35:23.080
But, we're never going to pay less for food,
unless, I mean, unless the government decides

00:35:23.080 --> 00:35:34.900
to subsidize all organic food. But that could
happen, but I see that there's even the ultimate

00:35:34.900 --> 00:35:46.600
way to do this. It's my own stimulus program.
Now we can talk about billions. So, I would

00:35:46.600 --> 00:35:55.370
put the money into schools to feed every child
at school, a breakfast, a lunch and an afternoon

00:35:55.370 --> 00:36:01.260
snack. And then I would give, which would
give money right back to the parents and the

00:36:01.260 --> 00:36:06.670
families because they would know that the
children were eating well, and that would

00:36:06.670 --> 00:36:13.060
help, that would be money in their pockets.
