00:36:13.060 --> 00:36:21.070
of the food in the schools. So that people
purchase the majority of food from local sustainable

00:36:21.070 --> 00:36:31.230
people which would stimulate the economy locally
and if they, if the stipulation was to buy

00:36:31.230 --> 00:36:40.330
all of their products from local and sustainable
people, just imagine what could happen, paper

00:36:40.330 --> 00:36:50.100
plates, we're talking about everything. But
Chez Panisse has served 500 people a day.

00:36:50.100 --> 00:36:57.540
We support maybe 85 farms, two farms in a
