00:47:27.650 --> 00:47:33.030
herbs. Whether it's, you know, I have lots
of things that are growing up every color,

00:47:33.030 --> 00:47:36.530
every kind, every shape. Because one meal,
I make an orange salad with purple things.

00:47:36.530 --> 00:47:44.840
And the next day, I may want a red salad up
with these early growth, with little tiny

00:47:44.840 --> 00:47:51.130
green basil. And you could eat tomato salad
every single day of this beautiful month of

00:47:51.130 --> 00:47:57.780
tomatoes and never get tired of them. Ever,
because it's just and then the third day,

00:47:57.780 --> 00:47:59.410
I'm eating every color all mixed together.
Just goes on like that. Yes?

